reviewText: For years I avoided the lot of blue collar comedy comics ...assuming they were low brow  and below my intellect..WRONG! These guys are clever and have the audience they have because beyond stereotypes they are as  intelligent in their own way as George Carlin or  Dennis  Miller. Beyond bathroom  humor  Larry mixes in takes on AL Gore and FORD not taking bailout money that I found topical and enjoyed as well. Pretty much everything in this hour program hit my funny bone but for 10 bucks even with a few misses (I appreciate everybodys tastes differ)I still believe you'd enjoy this. If  you enjoyed Git r Done and Morning Constitutionals then this should be an easy decision.
